Description: Egypt, Cairo street scene. Several adults and children walking in street, including European adult male at centre. Three-storey European building with sign saying "BRISTOL HOTEL" at rear. Medium: Gelatin silver print.
Producer name: Photographed by: John Frederick Clifford Hunt
Curator's comments: Circumstances: The Imperial War Museum holds photographs from the same collection with a more military content - see [HUN-] PIC DOC 66.
